{"word":"G2026 - ἐποικοδομέω - epoikodoméō - ep-oy-kod-om-eh'-o - Build thereon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐποικοδομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epoikodoméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-oy-kod-om-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Build thereon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டு, உறுதிப்படுத்து, அடை"},{"paragraph":"to build upon, build up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G3618 - οἰκοδομέω - oikodoméō - oy-kod-om-eh'-o/3618\">G3618</a>; to <i>build upon</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>rear up:</i> - build thereon (thereupon, on, upon).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2026/2026\">G2026</a>, <a href=\"#/G2731/2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732/2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G2733/2733\">G2733</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609/3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611/3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613/3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614/3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3615/3615\">G3615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3616/3616\">G3616</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617/3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3618/3618\">G3618</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619/3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620/3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621/3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622/3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3623/3623\">G3623</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624/3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925/4925\">G4925</a>"}]}